txt.en: The symbol on this token does not appear to be of Dunlending origin. Gwilum at Barnavon may be interested in studying it.

'This token disturbs me, [placeholder]. I have seen this symbol upon the trappings of the Warg-riders. It is not a symbol of my people, and I know not why the warriors of the Uch-lûth would carry such a thing.\n\n'It troubles me to think that my people might consider allying themselves with goblins and Wargs.'
'Have you found any evidence as regarding the origins of the Warg-riders?'
You found a strange token bearing a foreign symbol upon a Dunlending warrior.
Bring the Nâkhmau symbol to Gwilum in Barnavon
Gwilum is at the gate to Lower Barnavon.\n\nYou should bring the token you found to Gwilum.
